description: Have you been looking for the best in craft BBQ in the city of Columbus? Then look no further than Barrel & Boar!They bring their passion to the pit each and every day, making amazing meals that will have you coming back for more. If you like sliders, ribs, BBQ tacos, and all manner of savory BBQ eats, then we can guarantee that this truck will have your mouth watering in no time.Don't miss out on Ohio's latest and greatest addition to the street food scene, visit Barrel & Boar today.
name: Barrel & Boar
